76561198024583914,Recommended,227000,3551410,"Posted: 6 January, 2013",all,interploy,"Short (10-12hr), but good. If you're wanting a pure adventure game (think King's Quest) it's worth a look. Story is serious, but the sidekick and gamer inside jokes keep it from getting down. Only real complaint is you can't change the resolution, which is a shame because the graphics would be amazing at a higher res. They have a demo on the company site if you want to try it first."
