76561198004499559,Recommended,227000,2240487,"Posted: 28 December, 2012",all,Hero_Weasel,"Short but very good. Its set in a post apocolypse setting, with all robots. The story follows our hero and a robot built by said hero on a journy to get back somthing stolen from him...Its an adventure game, not a lot of action, most things are acomplished by trying to use items on things in the world, or on eachother. Most of the puzzles are pretty simple, and the game isnt very long. The story is very well writen and the voice acting is top notch. The games reselution is SUPER LOW, but the art work is still atractive....would have been nicer at a higher reselution but eh, what can you do.For $10 its kind of short (assumeing you get every puzzle right instantly, or dont want to see a diffrent ending that requiers you to play with diffrent outcomes) but is still very sweet."
